                    "difficulty": "Medium",
                    "answer": "4",
                    "question_type": 1,
                    "question": "设二维离散型随机变量的联合分布如下:\n\\begin{tabular}{|c|cccc|}\n\\hline$X \\backslash Y$ & 1 & 2 & 3 & 4 \\\\\n\\hline 1 & $1 / 4$ & 0 & 0 & $1 / 16$ \\\\\n\\hline 2 & $1 / 16$ & $1 / 4$ & 0 & $1 / 4$ \\\\\n\\hline 3 & 0 & $1 / 16$ & $1 / 16$ & 0 \\\\\n\\hline\n\\end{tabular}\n\n则 $P\\left\\{\\frac{1}{2}<X<\\frac{3}{2}, 0<Y<4\\right\\}, P\\{1 \\leq X \\leq 2,3 \\leq Y \\leq 4\\}$ 分别等于 ( ).",
                    "analysis": "$\\begin{aligned} P\\left\\{\\frac{1}{2}<X<\\frac{3}{2}, 0<Y<4\\right\\} &= P\\{X=1, Y=1\\}+P\\{X=1, Y=2\\}+P\\{X=1, Y=3\\} \\\\ &= \\frac{1}{4}+0+0=\\frac{1}{4} \\\\ P\\{1 \\leq X \\leq 2,3 \\leq Y \\leq 4\\} &= P\\{X=1, Y=3\\}+P\\{X=1, Y=4\\}+P\\{X=2, Y=3\\}+P\\{X=2, Y=4\\} \\\\ &= 0+\\frac{1}{16}+0+\\frac{1}{4}=\\frac{5}{16}. \\end{aligned}$",
